column1: IF ccr_testosterone_d is MF 0 AND ccr_tha_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_b_cortol_d is MF 1 AND ccr_pt_one_d is MF 2 AND ccr_b_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_the_d is MF 1 AND ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 0 AND ccr_cortisone_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 0  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
